            "answer_text": "I have been wanting to do this from a long time. Turns out, it\u2019s pretty simple. Here\u2019s how you do it: Log in to your Facebook and go to Setting > Apps and Websites. Here you will see a list of apps and websites where you've logged in through Facebook. Remove Goodreads from this list.Go to Goodreads Home page and click Forgot it? under password. Set a new password for your email ID and you're done!",
